              "kind": "plain",
              "text": "2776 - وَ رَوَى مُعَاوِيَةُ بْنُ عَمَّارٍ قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:61:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/61/4",
        "text": [
          " قَالَ لِي أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «إِذَا أَدْرَكَ اَلزَّوَالَ فَقَدْ أَدْرَكَ اَلْمَوْقِفَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.2776 - Mu'awiyah ibn Ammar narrated that Abu Abdullah (as) said to him:\n\"If someone reaches the standing (at Arafat) before the sun passes its zenith, they have attained the standing.\""
          ]
        }
      }
